            "faq_title": "Our Terms of Care & Use",
            "faq_des": "<p>Effective Date: 12/20/2025<br/><br/>Avant Toi, LLC dba Fleuriation (\"Company,\" \"we,\" \"our,\" or \"us\") is a skincare and wellness brand dedicated to formulating herbal, non-toxic products to restore and replenish the body. These Terms of Service (\"Terms\") govern your use of our website (https://www.fleuriation.com), products, and services (collectively, the \"Services\"). By using our products and services, you agree to these Terms.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_002": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
