            "faq_des": "<p>You must be at least 18 years old (or the age of majority in your state or country) to use our website, products, services, or make purchases. By using our website, products, or services, you confirm that you meet these requirements or have parental/guardian consent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_003": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Use of the Website & Services",
            "faq_des": "<p>A. You may use our website for personal, non-commercial purposes only.</p><p>B. You agree not to misuse our website, products, or services, attempt unauthorized access, or engage in unlawful or harmful activities.</p><p>C. You agree to provide accurate and current information when creating an account or making a purchase.</p><p>D. You may be required to provide information about yourself including your name, email address, and other personal information.</p><p>E. You agree not to impersonate someone else or provide (account information, an email address, or other personal information) other than your own.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_004": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Product Information & Disclaimer",
            "faq_des": "<p>A. Fleuriation formulates herbal, plant-based products for skincare and wellness.</p><p>B. No Medical Advice: Our products are not intended to diagnose, treat, cure, or prevent any medical condition. Consult a healthcare provider before use, especially if pregnant, nursing, or managing medical conditions.</p><p>C. All products should be used according to their instructions. Fleuriation is not responsible for misuse, allergic reactions, or adverse effects.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_005": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Orders, Payments, Pricing, & Discounts",
            "faq_des": "<p>A. Prices are listed in USD and are subject to change without notice.</p><p>B. All orders are subject to availability and acceptance.</p><p>C. Payments are processed securely through trusted third-party providers. We do not store payment information.</p><p>D. We reserve the right to refuse or cancel orders for any reason, including suspected fraud or policy violations.</p><p>E. When you purchase from Fleuriation, we collect only the necessary information like your name, address, and payment details to fulfill your order. We treat this information with care and integrity, partnering with trusted processors to keep it secure.</p><p>F. If you choose to engage with another business through our website, the terms of that transaction like payment, delivery, or refunds are between you and that merchant. While we aim to connect you with trusted partners, Fleuriation isn’t responsible for any issues that may result from those dealings.</p><p>G. Payment processors and merchants have their own policies, and we are not responsible for them. Some purchases may include additional terms from those parties or from us.</p><p>H. We encourage you to review their websites or contact them directly for more details. By making a purchase, you release Fleuriation, our trusted partners, and payment processors from any claims or damages related to your use of our website or products.</p><p>I. Your cart always shows the latest prices and includes any discounts you’ve applied. Prices may change, so the final price could differ from when you first added items.</p><p>J. Placing an item in your cart doesn’t guarantee the price. Since discounts are often limited-time, prices may change before you finish checking out and depend on product availability.</p><p>K. We do our best to keep prices accurate, but mistakes may occur. If an item is priced incorrectly, you may cancel your order or reach out to us at <a href=\"mailto:info@fleuriation.com\">info@fleuriation.com</a> for instructions.</p><p>L. Please Note: prices don’t include state sales tax. Your total, including any taxes, will be shown at checkout.</p><p>M. To keep offering you the best in herbal wellness, we may add new products or discontinue some over time. If a product is being discontinued, we’ll let you know in advance before it’s no longer available.</p><p>N. At times, we may offer special promotions or discounts for a limited time or to select customers. These may change or end at our discretion.</p><p>O. We honor only current and authorized promotions, even if shared on third-party websites.</p><p>P. Discounts cannot be combined with other offers, hold no cash value, and may not be sold or exchanged.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_006": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Shipping & Returns",
            "faq_des": "<p>Shipping times and rates vary based on your location and selected method. For details on returns, exchanges, and refunds, refer to our <a href=\"https://fleuriation.com/pages/shipping-policy-1\"><strong>Shipping</strong></a> & <a href=\"https://fleuriation.com/pages/refund-policy-1\"><strong>Return</strong></a> Policy.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_007": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Intellectual Property",
            "faq_des": "<p>All content on the Fleuriation website including logos, product designs, images, text, trademark, and other materials are owned by Fleuriation and protected by intellectual property laws. You may not copy, modify, distribute, or use our content without prior written consent.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_008": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Prohibited Conduct",
            "faq_des": "<p>You agree not to:</p><p>A. Use the website, products, and/or services for unlawful, fraudulent, or malicious purposes.</p><p>B. Attempt to gain unauthorized access to our systems or interfere with website functionality.</p><p>C. Post, upload, or transmit any harmful or offensive content.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_009": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Limitation of Liability",
            "faq_des": "<p>To the fullest extent permitted by law, Fleuriation will not be liable for:</p><p>A. Any indirect, incidental, or consequential damages arising from your use of our website, products, or services.</p><p>B. Any injury, reaction, or adverse effect resulting from product use.</p><p>C. You assume full responsibility for using our website, products, and services.</p><p>D. If you experience dissatisfaction with our website, product, or services, your primary solution is to email us at <a href=\"mailto:info@fleuriation.com\">info@fleuriation.com</a> or discontinue use.</p><p>E. Fleuriation is not liable for any losses or damages whether direct or indirect arising from your use of our website, products, or services.</p><p>F. For product concerns, your options are limited to those in our <a href=\"https://fleuriation.com/pages/refund-policy-1\"><strong>Return Policy</strong></a> or applicable warranties.</p><p>G. While we strive for excellence, we do not guarantee uninterrupted or error-free services. You agree to use them at your own risk.</p><p></p>"
          }
        },
