        "faq_012": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Notice to California Residents",
            "faq_des": "<p>In keeping with California’s Proposition 65, we are required to inform you that some products may contain trace amounts of chemicals associated with cancer or reproductive harm. While we don’t believe our products contain these in meaningful amounts, we provide this notice out of transparency and care for our customers. To comply with California’s Proposition 65, we notify you that some products may contain trace amounts of chemicals linked to cancer or reproductive harm. For questions, please contact us at: <a href=\"mailto:info@fleuriation.com\">info@fleuriation.com</a>.</p>"
